ŗźø─/└ łĮģ(70║Źw8+@Ū[IN arrayDistinct(promote(@c14 AS ARRAY(LONG))) SORTED] | INJOIN q0 -> { ISCAN(T4_COL3_VERSION [EQUALS q0] REVERSE) | MAP (version([_]) AS __ROW_VERSION, _.ID AS ID, _.COL1 AS COL1, _.COL3 AS COL3) }Ōdigraph G {
